// Phase 6: callable hardening showcase

surakṣitam .

vidhānam ṣaṭkam .
pratyāvartanam 6 .
samāpanam .

vidhānam yogaḥ a .
pratyāvartanam a .
samāpanam .

vidhānam yogaḥ a b .
pratyāvartanam a yoga b .
samāpanam .

vidhānam śuddhaḥ tri-yoga a b c .
pratyāvartanam a yoga b yoga c .
samāpanam .

vidhānam kālavyāpāre dviguṇana mūlya .
pratyāvartanam mūlya yoga mūlya .
samāpanam .

saṃskāraṃ anuvīkṣaṇam .
vidhānam sādhanaṃ abhivādana nāma .
darśanam nāma .
samāpanam .

vidhānam punarāvartanam saṅkhyā .
pratyāvartanam āhvānam punarāvartanam saṅkhyā .
samāpanam .

gaṇitam samāpanam-bandha āhvānam ṣaṭkam .
gaṇitam yukta āhvānam yogaḥ sapta .
gaṇitam vistarita āhvānam yogaḥ tri catur .
gaṇitam ekapūrva āṃśikam āhvānam tri-yoga eka .
gaṇitam navam āhvānam ekapūrva tri pañca .
gaṇitam phala āhvānam dviguṇana nava .

darśanam samāpanam-bandha .
darśanam yukta .
darśanam vistarita .
darśanam navam .
darśanam phala .
āhvānam abhivādana vākyam namaste iti .
